    {
      "parameters": {
        "promptType": "define",
        "text": "=Analyze the following blog post HTML content: {{ $('Cleanup HTML ').item.json.content }} Perform these checks: 1. Tone Check: Does it match \"Professional Peer\" tonality? Is it concise and efficient? 2. Readability Score: Is the content easy to read? (Flesch Reading Ease equivalent) 3. Keyword Density: Is the keyword \"{{ $('Parsing').item.json.slug }}\" used naturally (1-3% density)? 4. Human Content: Does it sound natural and human-written, not robotic? Return ONLY a JSON object: { \"toneScore\": 0-100, \"readabilityScore\": 0-100, \"keywordDensity\": 0-100, \"humanScore\": 0-100, \"overallScore\": 0-100, \"passed\": true/false, \"feedback\": \"Brief feedback\" } Pass threshold: overallScore >= 70",
        "options": {
          "systemMessage": "You are a content quality analyzer for Technology, IT and Corporate blog posts. Evaluate tone, readability, keyword usage, and human-like writing quality."
        }
      },
